","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有能力協調到唔撞區咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把區主動當選都唔擺資源落去打 寧願同其他泛民撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新西馮檢基, 我記一世呀呢條柒頭<br />\n屌佢老母臭閪玩空降<br />\n無票就一早死撚開啦"},{"pid":"7209348d40ae0d2be26e8cbaf2798f423281ca7d","tid":204994,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢攪乜衰乜<br />\n<br />\n我代共產黨多謝佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n摩訶無量喎<br />\n共產黨唔撚驚"},{"pid":"b850b88f55b262157416ed50e46789b43635fe5a","tid":204994,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雷動完就風雲 下一個會係咩</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">更進一步玩謝港豬民主，梗係&quot;中華英雄&quot;啦屌！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d8355b1faff323b5c0c666b9d13a7cfc5252d0f6","tid":204994,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:40:08.000Z","msg":"到底依件史前廢物幾撚時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3755242c042e723194c2a17df472c6950b18a605","tid":204994,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/33/Fung_Wan_movie_poster_1998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F33%2FFung_Wan_movie_poster_1998.jpg&h=757eaeb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94b3a52cedece0f0ad3389e155b1ade21964056f","tid":204994,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/04/17/6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F04%2F17%2F6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif&h=1a1f4dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aad5d52c66261801e597a4ba3f47de34251c212","tid":204994,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"瘋雲"},{"pid":"4c01b328f03761edd82e6a5e06965c87d412432b","tid":204994,"uid":95470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2019區選「風雲計劃」<br />\n（港大法律系副教授 戴耀廷）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由現在開始，就要開始籌募經費、招募及培訓風雲戰士，以應付2019年那場大戰。</blockquote><br />\n重點係叫你送錢比佢使"},{"pid":"cc61acbd511381e3b313e788c23d5401f96f3bc4","tid":204994,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:53:31.000Z","msg":"其實佢啲計劃幾好,但無乜可能實踐"},{"pid":"03431b027d0f6c3e7a1101ce91ef18be85c6ac23","tid":204994,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢啲計劃幾好,但無乜可能實踐</blockquote><br />\n理論黎講無錯<br />\n<br />\n但點去 achieve 係一個難題<br />\n<br />\nbtw 樓上果理一見係戴耀廷講就唔理三七廿一就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （其實我估無論邊個講咩佢地都會屌）"},{"pid":"b58a5a8e6b2f50630cff6ddf5665b9dfe24a9e5d","tid":204994,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4530d66b498ad72695220c68d12da3346cefa3e6","tid":204994,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"條友係老mk定老中二"},{"pid":"ef8931691953f8025613c6b7cff7e1e561390eff","tid":204994,"uid":23077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/04/17/6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F04%2F17%2F6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif&h=1a1f4dc3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n篇文講乜我無睇 入黎純粹為左睇呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7f167fccfe9816ecb21112ee87f3f4b6796eca","tid":204994,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"樓上班柒頭有咩方法對抗共匪呀咁<br />\n繼續上連登念力爭取真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d39ab59cd713c3cbfacfaaf94cad28432a0d49","tid":204994,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/04/17/6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F04%2F17%2F6596_20160417201244_57137dbc9f62a.gif&h=1a1f4dc3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n篇文講乜我無睇 入黎純粹為左睇呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩窮人生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ffd73f393703d8cffa0432ff96f7dec0f4066c","tid":204994,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上班柒頭有咩方法對抗共匪呀咁<br />\n繼續上連登念力爭取真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講其他，唔好搞風雲兩隻字得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經比謝天華套瘋暈搞到我有陰影"},{"pid":"abf3a97f8ccc4c2dd4037fd0bcb026d5a1d42467","tid":204994,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c90779b21117d63c3c02a42bf7257b97513c9f7b","tid":204994,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2019區選「風雲計劃」<br />\n（港大法律系副教授 戴耀廷）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由現在開始，就要開始籌募經費、招募及培訓風雲戰士，以應付2019年那場大戰。</blockquote><br />\n重點係叫你送錢比佢使</blockquote><br />\n培訓招募，上次咪出咗一堆所謂傘兵囉"},{"pid":"abe4cb1b5f456cb14a31a5dea90b17bf6e04e4aa","tid":204994,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2019區選「風雲計劃」<br />\n（港大法律系副教授 戴耀廷）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由現在開始，就要開始籌募經費、招募及培訓風雲戰士，以應付2019年那場大戰。</blockquote><br />\n重點係叫你送錢比佢使</blockquote><br />\n培訓招募，上次咪出咗一堆<del>所謂傘兵</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不死死士或逃兵</span></span></strong>囉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"71f79b3412deb0e5a648696a3dc92c806275ed54","tid":204994,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通靠本土派咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本土掟磚又話暴力冇目的 又怕坐<br />\n唔通你肯拎支ak上天安門咩<br />\n上面泛民有計劃理論又屌人鳩做投共(當然有大部分泛民真係<br />\n咁點呀 繼續返工等金仔炸撚到共產黨倒台呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cb221a9eae5af57c45b505a0373036fe7b6057","tid":204994,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:09:24.000Z","msg":"係個名同戴生個人既問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係令到<br />\n1. 每區都有非保皇既人，阻止保皇自動當選<br />\n2. 盡量唔撞區，減少保皇勝率<br />\n係應該要做"},{"pid":"5749a311f1df57f0331f7203e5d2f8bcdd5b111b","tid":204994,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"講啲老母係女人既道理<br />\n又唔講點去做<br />\n傻鳩都識啦"},{"pid":"24669343be97f0f9c4262454729552fb1c47b4bf","tid":204994,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實佢啲計劃幾好,但無乜可能實踐</blockquote><br />\n理論黎講無錯<br />\n<br />\n但點去 achieve 係一個難題<br />\n<br />\nbtw 樓上果理一見係戴耀廷講就唔理三七廿一就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （其實我估無論邊個講咩佢地都會屌）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪即係同共產一樣<br />\n<br />\n理論嚟講無錯</blockquote><br />\n簡單多票制明明有利民主派但好多人懶得投票/因為建制議員有資源做到嘢 所以建制唔自動當選都贏到<br />\n但當同政治掛返勾 區選立會化 有得贏都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d435529c6303193d061bb936078f2692c09da85","tid":204994,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係個名同戴生個人既問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係令到<br />\n1. 每區都有非保皇既人，阻止保皇自動當選<br />\n2. 盡量唔撞區，減少保皇勝率<br />\n係應該要做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上係咁<br />\n但係有啲區好撚多廢老同辣殺師一早埋哂邊<br />\n唔係話派條友出黎就得<br />\n利申 廢老區議會選區"},{"pid":"afd6778bf78f1ac7ee341f0e8d79efb6d061848f","tid":204994,"uid":36642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"咁快叫人課金<br />\n<br />\n一陣課金班友俾ICAC用Cap554告就好笑"},{"pid":"2f78d48435e23bf9b72470ae96e32de4d406dc00","tid":204994,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"support風雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5366d51cf1be8b7baa53c863729f54e9773bd249","tid":204994,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔通靠本土派咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本土掟磚又話暴力冇目的 又怕坐<br />\n唔通你肯拎支ak上天安門咩<br />\n上面泛民有計劃理論又屌人鳩做投共(當然有大部分泛民真係<br />\n咁點呀 繼續返工等金仔炸撚到共產黨倒台呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19a66e4e0b8cba265974159b2df41be3bab5d85","tid":204994,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"49bff60cf66a9939a3731d61de85f0f9fceaa6e3","tid":204994,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://pic.qiantucdn.com/58pic/18/30/34/34X58PICg