9e3ae7","tid":204994,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實戴妖個雷動都係成功<br />\n立法會選舉幫犯民攞盡議席，而且踢走佢哋認為最篤眼篤鼻嘅熱狗、教主</blockquote><br />\n客觀嚟講，晒咗好多票喺朱凱迪度，整死咗李卓人添。"},{"pid":"e6faf35cf371b851124e12c95f9811f8c70f2467","tid":204994,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"你雷動雷撚死新西仲好意思再提策略選民？我屌你老母啦！<br />\n<br />\n何況到時比你地拎到選委啦咪又係拎黎比你地尸位素餐，打壓異己，我何苦幫你作嫁衣裳？"},{"pid":"fcda253dfbafd0930a377a71623801b91b8dfac4","tid":204994,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係個名同戴生個人既問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係令到<br />\n1. 每區都有非保皇既人，阻止保皇自動當選<br />\n2. 盡量唔撞區，減少保皇勝率<br />\n係應該要做</blockquote><br />\n撞區咪又係逼你走,屈你係鬼鎅票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣整個有公信力 大家都認同既協調機制  協調每區都淨係得一個非建制人參選  然後所有票投晒落去 先有機會</blockquote><br />\n個協調機制啲條約本身就on9，<br />\n新人跟足嘅話，基本上唔使玩。"},{"pid":"34b5d5969eb765a738a0840a686d6c5324aa355a","tid":204994,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/09/02/224624_87fc927639c321425ce9fc6bcddeee9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F09%2F02%2F224624_87fc927639c321425ce9fc6bcddeee9e.jpg&h=5806bf28&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6e440d42b1ee9c90a23630b413feb4f98b0ebc","tid":204994,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"雲無痕　來去若霧　將背影鋪血路<br />\n未似風不息　搖蕩了劫數<br />\nWoo <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Wo</span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">woo</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">woo</span>"},{"pid":"078fe7b8e19e952ff61